---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<Layout title="CSPB Self-Guided Info Session" showSidebar={false}>
  <section class="mx-auto grid min-h-[75vh] max-w-6xl items-center gap-10 py-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_420px]">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-yellow-700">CU Boulder CSPB</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-950 md:text-7xl">
        Self-guided information session
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-700">
        Get the core information from the live CSPB information session on your own schedule. Review the program overview, curriculum, online learning format, admissions requirements, tuition, career outcomes, and next steps.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <CTAButton href="/register/" label="Start the info session" />
        <CTAButton href="/dashboard/" label="Continue as returning visitor" variant="secondary" />
      </div>
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-neutral-500">
        Mockup note: the production version will use CU Boulder Qualtrics for intake before returning visitors to the dashboard.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="rounded-[2rem] border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-neutral-950">What you’ll find</h2>
      <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-700">
        <li>Short video-supported modules.</li>
        <li>Admissions and prerequisite guidance.</li>
        <li>Curriculum, course, and pacing information.</li>
        <li>Tuition, transfer credit, and non-degree options.</li>
        <li>Clear next steps for applying or talking with CSPB.</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>
</Layout>
